<!DOCTYPE HTML>

<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <title>Life Post</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html" charset="UTF-8"/>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

{{> layout/navigation}}
<div class="mt-5"></div>
<div class="container" id="my-page-space">
  <div class="row col-md-4 mx-auto">
    <div class="card p-0 border-primary">
      <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">회원정보</div>
      <ul id="member-info-box-space" class="list-group list-group-flush">
        <li class="list-group-item border-primary">
          <div id="sign-in-date-title" class="info-title h4">가입일자</div>
          <div id="sign-in-date" class="info-contents-class"></div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item border-primary">
          <div id="email-title" class="info-title h4">이메일</div>
          <div id="email" class="info-contents-class"></div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item border-primary">
          <div id="social-title" class="info-title h4">소셜</div>
          <div id="social-type" class="info-contents-class"></div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item border-primary">
          <div id="stamp-count-title" class="info-title h4">보유한 스탬프 수</div>
          <div id="stamp-count" class="info-contents-class"></div>
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
          <div class="d-flex">
            <div class="flex-fill"></div>
            <button id="withdraw-btn" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                    data-bs-target="#withdraw-modal">회원탈퇴
            </button>
            <div class="flex-fill"></div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="withdraw-modal" tabindex="-1"
     aria-labelledby="withdraw-label"
     aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h1 class="modal-title fs-3 text-primary" id="withdraw-modal-label">Withdraw</h1>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body" id="modal-content-body">
        <div class="alert-class">회원을 탈퇴하시면 회원님의 정보가 삭제됩니다.</div>
        <div class="alert-class">탈퇴 이후에는 데이터 복구 또한 불가능합니다.</div>
        <div class="alert-class">그래도 탈퇴하시겠습니까?</div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <label>
          <input id="agree-check-box" class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="agree"
                 value="true"> 동의합니다.
        </label>
        <button id="withdraw-ok-btn" class="btn btn-danger" disabled>탈퇴</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script type="module" src="/js/mypage.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-HwwvtgBNo3bZJJLYd8oVXjrBZt8cqVSpeBNS5n7C8IVInixGAoxmnlMuBnhbgrkm"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>